This is a custom distribution of UnitTest++, version 1.4, with a CMake-based
build system.

The original README file of UnitTest++ was renamed as 'UNITTEST-CPP-README'.


This distribution don't contain the unit tests of UnitTest++, only the library
itself.


UnitTest++'s license is unchanged: this library is free software. You may copy,
distribute, and modify it under the terms of the license contained in the file
COPYING distributed with this package. This license is the same as the MIT/X
Consortium license.
